---
title: Quick Sausage Bolognese with Spinach, Spaghetti, and Parmesan
description: Everyone loves a homemade Bolognese, but not everyone has three hours to spend in the kitchen. That’s why we developed this flavour-packed shortcut! Parmesan cheese gives the sauce an umami boost in no time at all.
